/doc:  Documentation Directory.

./Copying       Copyright information on the mudlib and imported code
./LPC           LPC manuals written by Descartes@Nightmare
./driver        MudOS driver documentation
./help          Help files for use with the 'help' command
./man           MudOS and mudlib manual pages for use with 'man' command
./mudlib        Misc. mudlib info; systems, style guide, etc.
./projects      Development directory.  Serves as a first place to document
                new project ideas for discussion before coding begins.
